}
</imiona>

11.

Wyrażenie ścieżkowe:

<DataOnTheWeb>
{
  doc("../Downloads/xquery/bib/bib.xml")//book[title='Data on the Web']
}
</DataOnTheWeb>

Klauzula where:

<DataOnTheWeb>
{
    for $book in doc("../Downloads/xquery/bib/bib.xml")//book where $book/title = 'Data on the Web' return $book
}
</DataOnTheWeb>

12.

<Data>
{
  for $book in doc("../Downloads/xquery/bib/bib.xml")//book where contains($book/title, 'Data')
for $title in $book/title
for $author in $book/author
return 
<nazwisko>
  {$author/last/text()}
</nazwisko>
}
</Data>

13.

